name: .WIL File Extension
summary: Learn about .WIL files and view a list of programs that open them.

description: List of disk images generated by WinImage, a disk imaging program; created using the Batch Assistant within WinImage; may be used to export multiple .IMA files or a single .WLZ file.

content: A WIL file can also be imported into WinImage to load a set of disk images into the Batch Assistant.
